#(@) Compiling and installing the ldapcppei library

Requirement: the openldap package "libldap2-dev" must be installed.
The "fakeroot" package is also requied to: "make debian"...

Example of unpacking the distribution :

	% cd /tmp
	% tar xzf libldapcppei-${version}.tgz
	% cd libldapcppei/

Compiling the library:

	% make

Installing the library:

	% make install

Installation of sources:

	% make installsrc

Uninstall library and sources:

	% make uninstall

Make a debian package:

	% make debian

Install the debian package:

	% sudo dpkg -i libldapcppei-${version}.deb

